  /usr/local/bin/vim -Nu <(cat << VIMRC
  filetype off
  set rtp+=vader.vim
  set rtp+=.
  set rtp+=after
  filetype plugin indent on
  syntax enable
    VIMRC) -c 'Vader! test/*' > /dev/null

Execute (Sleep for 1 second):
  sleep 1

Then:
  AssertEqual getloclist(0), []
